  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      There are different medicinal and non medicinal methods to control labor pain. Today, much
      attention has been on non medicinal methods because of limitations and complications of
      medical procedures. Virtual reality is a new and promising method of diversion of mind that
      may have an impact on labor pain. This study was conducted to determine the effect of
      virtual reality on the first stage of labor pain.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
